data.description: Beautiful newly painted 4-Bedroom, 2.5 bath home located in the desirable NW Canyon Neighborhood. Walking distance to Dry Canyon Access, schools, and parks. Open concept  complete with gourmet kitchen, large island, pantry, stainless-steel appliances and dining area. Great room with a gas fireplace perfect for entertaining family and guests.  A bedroom/office with French doors, 1/2 bath, and laundry room complete the downstairs.Upstairs the primary suite boasts cathedral ceilings, ensuite bathroom, walk-in closet, new flooring, and step-in shower along with spectacular mountain views.  A large hall skylight, 2 large bedrooms and a full bath with skylight finish off the upstairs.Outside you'll find a fully fenced backyard oasis perfect for outdoor entertaining! Large concrete stamped patio, hot-tub, pergola, Koi Pond, fruit trees, sprinkler system and raised beds. RV/Boat cover complete with it's own gate. 3 car garage.MOTIVATED sellers offing $10,000 towards closing costs.
